author: gturrell
msg: [woden-139] changed ValidateWSDL20 to accept two additional args from the build.xml task invocations, "catalog" and "baseURI",

which are then used by the URI resolver to set o.a.w.resolver.simpleresolver.catalog and o.a.w.resolver.simpleresolver.baseURIs properties. This removes the need to specify system property values on the jvm command line of the
ant client. The string values passed from the build.xml are local file and directory location respectively.
